      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. that's a good start. but i'm worried my professor might argue that meritocracy is a better way to handle things—like the idea that people should just work hard and earn what they deserve. how can i address that in my paper? i want to show why the meritocracy argument is basically just a way to ignore systemic issues.",
