      "content": "that makes sense. i want to make the section about meritocracy really impactful. can you expand on that part where you say it's a \"myth\"? like, how can i frame the idea that the belief in meritocracy is actually used as a tool to keep the current racial hierarchy in place? i want to make it clear that it's not just a misunderstanding, but a way to justify why people stay poor.",
